    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">DEFINITION: Relates something to its destination place.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">EXAMPLE: A letter has an address indicating its destination; a segment of a delivery route terminates at a delivery location; a trail terminates at an intersection with another trail.</rdfs:comment>
